item.description: Keep it simple, stupid. starting a blog Trying to satisfy my endless urge to show people around me the results of my hobbies they don’t care about, I have finally decided to whip up a blog. Who will read this? Probably only people I beg to. But maybe someday someone will find actual value in my passion. In the mean time, I’m sorry i coerced you into reading this my dear friend/family member/girlfriend.
